STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Robert M. MURPHY, Appellant. WD 79926 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: May 1, 2018 Jedd Schneider, Columbia, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Julia Neidhardt, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division One: Lisa White Hardwick, P.J., Thomas H. Newton, and Cynthia L. Martin, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mr. Robert M. Murphy appeals the conviction by a Cass County jury of first-degree child molestation, § 566.067, for which he was sentenced to fifteen years' imprisonment. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
